# Goals

---

## AutoDown-G1 Block-based Markdown editor with TipTap
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:autodown
**Depends on:** UiSystem-G1

- [x] TipTap-based editor component (`AutoDownEditor.vue`)
- [x] Slash menu, bubble menu, and table menu
- [x] Custom extensions for tables, row resizing, task lists
- [x] Serialize/deserialize to Markdown-compatible HTML

## AutoDown-G2 Live preview side-by-side with raw Markdown
**Status:** in_progress
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:autodown
**Depends on:** AutoDown-G1

- [x] Basic live preview rendering
- [ ] Synchronized scroll between editor and preview
- [ ] Bidirectional selection sync

## AutoDown-G3 Spec-aware templates and IAL table storage
**Status:** draft
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:autodown
**Depends on:** Specs-G1, AutoDown-G1

- [ ] Template snippets for spec categories (Goals, Architecture, Designs, etc.)
- [ ] Inline Attribute List (IAL) support for structured tables
- [ ] Auto-complete spec ID references
